It was a blast having @_killacam back in the building. Different purpose but same passion. I enjoyed our discussions on art, philosophy and photography. It was a reminder to me of how passion can fuel and reignite purpose. Following joy and having courage to recognize when that joy isn’t present. The perspectives I gained further reinforced the connectedness we all share and a desire to focus and celebrate those things.  Appreciate @lindseymnsports for taking time to cover Cam’s visit. You can visit the link in my bio to read. Also give @_killacam and @_theomnicollective a follow 🙏🏻
